          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjn7-deihqGrC0EtD1hWU5-s3ZJc0eY-RxzVnVXqhQ-CJrNsCyBF8w54tqI0bMpgYZWbsnlPt8e1RlGTNall7QXTVLTe43mey_4W6WeQ7lvQqNJ2pc3aR0C8MLhgghbbvkJCXRfW6-dE7BIJTaNlfYHOh_YjNbSrIjKADQCNYGcjq2eYz8jZJQwCAKa8g/w381-h634/IMG-20230226.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='2541329510772586152' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='8266421870288263738' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='8266421870288263738'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://proletaricomunisti.blogspot.com/2023/02/lintervento-di-un-compagno-di-proletari.html'>pc 25 febbraio - L'Intervento di un compagno di proletari comunisti alla manifestazione di Genova contro la guerra</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
